    <div class="tn-note">
      <strong>&#x1f4dd; Cultural Note:</strong> The words “prayer” and “request” mean basically the same thing and emphasize that he is sincere as he makes his request. Solomon refers to himself as “your servant” to show that he respects Yahweh. This can be stated in first person. Alternate translation: [respect me, your servant, as I make this request] (See also: [[
    </div>
    <div class="tn-note">
